OL,3,CSeasonal workers on UK farms given
OL,4,C'unhealthy and dangerous' accommodation
OL,6,FAn ITV News investigation has found
OL,7,Fworkers on some farms are living in
OL,8,Fhomes riddled with mould and dampness,
OL,9,FCorrespondent Peter Smith reports
OL,11,FSeasonal workers on British farms are
OL,12,Fbeing given substandard accommodation
OL,13,Fand "unacceptable" living conditions,
OL,14,Fan ITV News investigation has found.
OL,16,FFootage obtained in our investigation
OL,17,Fshows evidence of mould and dampness
OL,18,Fon the walls of an old, leaky caravan
OL,19,Fat one location in Essex.
