OL,6,F"There weren't even enough beds - I
OL,7,Fhad to sleep sitting on a chair," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"Then they gave me an old sofa from
OL,11,Fthe barn that smelled of cat urine. If
OL,12,Fwe complained, they told us this is
OL,13,Fall that was available for us.
OL,15,F"Sometimes they were shouting at us,
OL,16,Ftelling us to work faster, even though
OL,17,Fwe were at the limit of our
OL,18,Fcapabilities. The relationship felt
OL,19,Flike slaves."
