OL,6,FThe owner of Leabank Nursery has
OL,7,Fdenied the allegations ITV News put to
OL,8,Fhim.
OL,10,FGregorio's Produce told us, "We do
OL,11,Faccept that the caravans that were
OL,12,Fused may require refurbishment."
OL,14,F"We do not at present intend to
OL,15,Frecruit seasonal workers again," they
OL,16,Fadded. "But if we do, we will ensure
OL,17,Fthat decorative refurbishment takes
OL,18,Fplace and any damp or mould issues are
OL,19,Fresolved."
