OL,6,FBut the farm in Essex is not the only
OL,7,Fplace we found concerns about
OL,8,Faccommodation.
OL,10,FIn the northeast of Scotland,
OL,11,FCastleton in Aberdeenshire is one of
OL,12,Fthe country's biggest, most
OL,13,Fprestigious fruit farms.
OL,15,FFamily run, it is owned by Ross and
OL,16,FAnna Mitchell.
