OL,3,CSeasonal workers on UK farms given
OL,4,C'unhealthy and dangerous' accommodation
OL,6,FThey've had a visit from royalty in
OL,7,Frecent years, and their company
OL,8,Fwebsite boasts that you'll see their
OL,9,Ffruit on the shelves at major
OL,10,Fsupermarkets such as Marks and
OL,11,FSpencer, Tesco, Waitrose, and Lidl.
OL,13,FHowever, workers have told us about
OL,14,F"overcrowding" in the static caravan
OL,15,Faccommodation provided to seasonal
OL,16,Fworkers.
OL,18,FITV News has obtained footage showing
OL,19,Ftwo people - sometimes strangers -
OL,20,Fsleeping almost side by side in small
OL,21,Fcaravan bedrooms.
