OL,6,FThe workers tell us they do a physical
OL,7,Fjob by day, and then they "must sleep
OL,8,Fin one position because there is
OL,9,Fbarely room to move" for the six
OL,10,Fmonths they live on Castleton Farm.
OL,12,FThere's also evidence of the furniture
OL,13,Fin the caravans being aged, in some
OL,14,Fcases clearly damaged.
