OL,6,FITV News has also learned how a two-
OL,7,Fbedroom caravan at Castleton is being
OL,8,Frented out for approximately #1,200
OL,9,Fper month.
OL,11,FWe checked and this is well above the
OL,12,Fgoing rate for two-bed accommodation
OL,13,Fin the area.
OL,15,FFor context, a modern two-bedroom
OL,16,Fmodern apartment is commonly listed at
OL,17,Fless than half that price in the
OL,18,Fnearest towns.
