OL,6,F"There's no privacy - you lose your
OL,7,Fdignity living like this," one worker
OL,8,Fat Castleton told us under the
OL,9,Fcondition of anonymity.
OL,11,FDespite paying such high rent already,
OL,12,Fthese workers told they have also been
OL,13,Fthreatened with a #100 fine if the
OL,14,Fcaravan is deemed to be untidy and
OL,15,Fthey say they face weekly inspections.
OL,17,F"We came here to do a job but this is
OL,18,Fnot how we expected workers in Great
OL,19,FBritain would be treated," the worker
OL,20,Fsaid.
