OL,6,F"It feels like we are being
OL,7,Fdiscriminated against."
OL,9,FWe can report that seasonal workers
OL,10,Fare not being given equal protections
OL,11,Fin law, and that is due to a legal
OL,12,Floophole identified in our
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,FCaravan accommodation housing this
OL,16,Fmany people should normally require
OL,17,FHMO licences, and would normally be
OL,18,Fsubject to inspections by local
OL,19,Fauthorities - but caravans for
OL,20,Fseasonal farm workers are specifically
OL,21,Fexempt for this.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
