OL,7,FExecutive, who told us, "HSE has no
OL,8,Fpowers to deal with living conditions
OL,9,Fsuch as overcrowding of accommodation."
OL,11,FThe power to create a change in the
OL,12,Flaw for Scotland is devolved, so we
OL,13,Fshowed our footage from Castleton to
OL,14,FScotland's First Minister who called
OL,15,Fit "deeply troubling".
OL,17,F"Those conditions look unacceptable,"
OL,18,FJohn Swinney said in response to the
OL,19,Fevidence we presented to him.
